=== Spec Example 7.1. Alias Nodes
--- from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2786448
--- tags: spec alias

--- in-yaml
First occurrence: &anchor Foo
Second occurrence: *anchor
Override anchor: &anchor Bar
Reuse anchor: *anchor

--- in-json
{
  "First occurrence": "Foo",
  "Second occurrence": "Foo",
  "Override anchor": "Bar",
  "Reuse anchor": "Bar"
}

